snippet.title: AFK Arena x The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Due to a teleporting gone wrong, Geralt the Witcher and the sorceress Yennefer found themselves stranded in Esperia. They must take great care as they navigate through the different forces at play in this wild, strange world.
